{"tid":1772987,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"泛民斥警犯眾憎 促加薪獨立審議","createTime":"2019-12-07T06:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T06:48:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c80c947f0b648d3742f6ca01fdd1257b9a62107f","tid":1772987,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/4GSL6X7EJQIMJRQ46P6R6OGDV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2F4GSL6X7EJQIMJRQ46P6R6OGDV4%2F&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrufE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=a8c467b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191207%2F4GSL6X7EJQIMJRQ46P6R6OGDV4%2F&h=a0ec4485\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191207/4GSL6X7EJQIMJRQ46P6R6OGDV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n泛民斥警犯眾憎 促加薪獨立審議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191207/large/1575647917_bfcd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191207%2Flarge%2F1575647917_bfcd.gif&h=707ddbed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n立會財委會昨商討公務員加薪議程，黃碧雲（左）直指警隊不應加人工；右為鄺俊宇。王子俊攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警暴未除，政府昨日向立法會財委會申請124億元撥款，為包括警隊在內的公務員加薪。民主派議員炮轟警隊近月表現惡劣，要求抽起警隊的加薪申請，斥政府要其他公務員「攬炒」。公務員事務局局長羅智光反對民主派要求，指公務員加薪撥款一直涵蓋所有公務員部門，沒有理由偏離既定機制。<br />\n<br />\n誓追究警暴<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：飛行服務隊 懲教 受累評分跌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會財委會昨日審議公務員加薪撥款，公民黨楊岳橋指，早前政府以有議員關注為由，要撤回大學的醫療教學設施，如今社會有強烈聲音反對警察加薪，為何政府卻將撥款「強闖」立法會。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨尹兆堅亦指，全社會都關注警方加薪問題，批評政府對於大學撥款和警員加薪是雙重標準，「你根本係頭搖又尾擺」。民主黨黃碧雲指無意阻礙其他公務員加薪，但警察「犯眾憎」，以「曱甴」稱呼示威者，質疑「警隊濫暴濫告，都可以照加人工咩？」<br />\n<br />\n羅智光指出，公務員加薪事宜一直按機制涵蓋所有公務員部門，沒有理由偏離既定機制。他指如果議員對警隊個別事件有意見，可由其他渠道跟進。<br />\n<br />\n至於有警員稱示威者為「曱甴」，羅智光指部門首長已作出跟進，坦言不同意用貶義的詞語批評他人，並呼籲各方以包容、彼此尊重的態度進行溝通。<br />\n<br />\n此外，民主派立法會議員聯同逾300位來自十八區的現任和候任區議員，向政府、財委會全體議員及全港市民發出聯署信，要求政府由公務員加薪議程中抽起警隊作獨立審議，繼而否決警隊加薪，作為追究警暴的第一步，以行動告誡警隊。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳嘉裕"},{"pid":"85a294c371de80df1060290568b306776ee956c5","tid":1772987,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}